coverageTab.title: Coverage

overviewTab.content:
Cyclists, get ready to hit the trail in South America with this unique routing-capable mapping product, compiled using third-party data suppliers, including the community-generated OpenStreetMap (OSM) database.

  • Includes searchable points of interest (restaurants, hotels, hostels, trains stations, etc.), cities, addresses and more
  • Includes turn-by-turn directions to your destination(s)
  • Includes cycling, tour cycling and mountain biking options to select the appropriate route for the type of cycling you do, taking you on paved roads, unpaved roads, or on paths and trails
